 ---------------------------------------------
France             Pounds 33.0m
Germany            Pounds 20.0m
Italy              Pounds 20.0m
UK                 Pounds 12.0m
Spain              Pounds  8.0m
Switzerland        Pounds  5.4m
Netherlands        Pounds  3.0m
Austria            Pounds  3.0m
Belgium            Pounds  2.4m
