Agriculture         32.7   35.3   39.6
Regional aid         9.1   18.6   29.3
Industry &amp; other     1.9    4.0    6.9
Foreign policy       1.4    3.6    6.3
Administration       5.9    4.0    4.0
Reserves             0.0    1.0    1.4
Total               51.0   66.6   87.5
