TUNISIA'S FIRST first privately owned and managed mining project, at
Bougrine in the province of Kev, has cleared a substantial hurdle by winning
USDollars 16.1m of financial support from the International Finance
Corporation, the World Bank's private-sector financing offshoot.
A German financial institution, Deutsche Investitions und
